2.4.4
- Fixed regular ender effect cloud making a pillar.
- Implemented a new Message API (internally).
- Renamed a few configs and storage keys.
- If an effect item despawns or is destroyed, it subtracts 1 from the number of those effects that have been crafted.
- Fixed the way apophis applies skins and nametags (it works on rejoin now).
- Fixed the invis death message modification so that it works based on the infuse effect, not the potion effect.
- Redid the action bar code.  It stays centered now.
- Fixed an issue with the ender effect whining in console about an event.
- Thief effect actually hides people from tablist
- Effect-based item enchantments get reverted to their original levels when stashed or dropped.
- The cooldown configs now represent the number of seconds the effect is inactive after the spark duration runs out.